add_alignments          Add an alignment to a file
add_outgroup_to_phylogeny
                        Adds an outgroup to a phylogeny
add_pbd_output          Adds a pbd_sim result to a file
add_posteriors          Add BEAST2 posteriors to a file
add_species_trees_with_outgroup
                        Add a species tree with outgroup to a file
branch_sorter           sorts branches for the NRBS analysis
check_progress          Function that shows how much parameter files
                        are present, and how far the pipeline has
                        gotten
collect_file_gammas     Collects the gamm statistics of all phylogenies
                        belonging to a parameter file in the
                        melted/uncast/long form
collect_gamma_statistics
                        Collects the gamma statistics of all
                        phylogenies in the melted/uncast/long form
collect_parameters      Creates tidy data of all parameter files
collect_posterior_filenames
                        Collect posterior filenames
collect_posterior_gammas
                        Collect the gamma statistics of the BEAST2
                        posteriors
collect_posterior_nltt_values
                        Collect the nLTT values of the BEAST2
                        posteriors
collect_species_tree_gammas
                        Collect the gamma statistics of the species
                        trees with outgroup
collect_species_tree_nltts
                        Collect the nLTT values of the species trees
                        with outgroup
convert_alignment_to_beast_input_file
                        Convert an alignment and parameters to a BEAST
                        XML input file
convert_alignment_to_beast_posterior
                        Convert an alignment to a BEAST2 XML input file
convert_alignment_to_fasta
                        Convert an alignment (of type DNAbin) to a
                        FASTA file
convert_phylogeny_to_alignment
                        Converts a phylogeny to a random DNA alignment
extract_erg             Extract the ERG ('Extinction Rate of a Good
                        species') parameter value from a file
extract_eri             Extract the ERI ('Extinction Rate of an
                        Incipient species') parameter value from a file
extract_scr             Extract the SCR ('Speciation Completion Rate')
                        parameter value from a file
extract_sirg            Extract the SIRG ('Speciation Initial Rate of a
                        Good species') parameter value from a file
extract_siri            Extract the SIRI ('Speciation Initial Rate of
                        an Incipient species') parameter value from a
                        file
find_beast_bin_path     Find the path of the BEAST2 binary file
find_beast_jar_path     Find the path of the BEAST2 jar file
find_beast_posterior_test_filename
                        Find the path of known-to-be-valid BEAST2
                        posterior file
find_path               Finds the full pathof a file
get_phylogeny_crown_age
                        Obtain the crown age of a phylony
is_alignment            Determines if the input is an alignment of type
                        DNAbin
is_beast_posterior      Determines if the input is a BEAST2 posterior
is_pbd_sim_output       Does not use pbd_sim()$stree, but generates
                        these like PBD does
is_phylogeny            Checks if the input is a phylogeny
is_valid_file           Checks if a file is a valid parameter file
is_whole_number         Checks if x is a single, whole-number variable
load_parameters_from_file
                        Load parameters from file
normalized_rooted_branch_score
                        calculates the normalized rooted branch score
plot_alignments         Plot alignments
plot_extant_incipient_tree
                        Plot the extant inicipient species tree
plot_posterior_nltts    Plot multiple BEAST2 posteriors
plot_posterior_sample_nltts
                        Plot the nLTTs of the posterior
plot_posterior_samples
                        Plot a random posterior phylogeny
plot_species_tree_with_outgroup
                        Plot
plot_species_tree_with_outgroup_nltt
                        Plot species_tree_with_outgroup_nltt
read_file               Read a parameter (.RDa) file
sample_species_trees_from_pbd_sim_output
                        Samples species trees from PBD::pbd_sim its
                        output It does not use pbd_sim()$stree, but
                        generates these like PBD does.
save_parameters_to_file
                        Creates a valid parameter file
show_parameter_files    Creates a nice knitr::table to show one or more
                        parameter files
